2. THE OASIS ETHICAL COVENANT & IMPACT GRANT (ODS/SDG)
   In addition to the terms of the GNU AGPLv3, the "Oasis Swarm Architect" 
   offers a special "Impact Grant" to foster positive social transformation.

   A. ALIGNMENT WITH SUSTAINABLE DEVELOPMENT GOALS (SDGs/ODS)
      Entities that can demonstrate strict alignment with the following United 
      Nations SDGs are eligible for a free Enterprise License:
      
      - ODS 4:  Quality Education (Educaci贸n de Calidad)
      - ODS 8:  Decent Work & Economic Growth (Trabajo Decente)
      - ODS 9:  Industry, Innovation & Infrastructure (Industria e Innovaci贸n)
      - ODS 12: Responsible Consumption (Producci贸n Responsable)
      - ODS 13: Climate Action (Acci贸n por el Clima)
      - ODS 16: Peace, Justice & Strong Institutions (Paz y Justicia)
      - ODS 17: Partnerships for the Goals (Alianzas)

   B. THE SOCIAL REINVESTMENT PLEDGE
      To activate this Impact Grant, the entity implies a moral commitment:
      "Resources and capital saved through the efficiency of this software 
      shall be partially redirected towards social works, fostering positive 
      human values, or furthering the aforementioned SDGs."

